{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2897159, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "呜呜呜最近也想找实习，可以安利下是哪家吗", "timestamp": 1636453744, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897165, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在劝run党的自嗨里，如果run真那么好为啥ta要到处宣扬给自己增加竞争呢？", "timestamp": 1636453792, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897167, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "众所周知，外企是中国最不性别歧视的地方\n", "timestamp": 1636453812, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897181, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897167, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 附议", "timestamp": 1636453951, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897182, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897167, "tag": null, "text": "怎么不去国企看看，有的国企连三清女博士的简历都不要不给面试", "timestamp": 1636453973, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897167, "tag": null, "text": "以及选调生，之前清一色的清华大学，男，哎", "timestamp": 1636453990, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897189, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897165, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不是一届的有什么可竞争的，而且国外华人更多自己过得更好", "timestamp": 1636454024, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897185, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 附议", "timestamp": 1636454052, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897185, "tag": null, "text": "对女性的歧视在每个人的潜意识里", "timestamp": 1636454070, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897206, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897185, "tag": null, "text": "有些事情，也许不是刻意要歧视，但是确实存在。甚至女性也在歧视自己。", "timestamp": 1636454103, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897220, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "救命，秋招女生在这里，我相信每一个经历过求职季的女生都或多或少有体会。远的不说，看看选调职位表里“限男性”和“限女性”的比例吧。不要身边即世界。", "timestamp": 1636454214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897233, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897185, "tag": null, "text": "举个例子，当我们在树洞里看到一些很专业很有前瞻性的言论，本能地就会认为是男性发出的，而不会想到是女性发出的。初高中的时候我们本能地觉得文科班很混乱，那些女生天天勾心斗角（事实也如此，但那么多文科班里总有不是这样的女生），这也是一种隐性歧视。在岗位上，可能你没看到怀孕的女性，但女性能怀孕，这是领导者对她们的歧视的很大根源。", "timestamp": 1636454328, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897259, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897220, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 希望我的经历能给你一些参考，或许外企是个不错的选择？", "timestamp": 1636454524, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897268, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897233, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 数学期望=歧视？", "timestamp": 1636454574, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897276, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897233, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 不想讨论这些高深的问题，只是提一下我的经历，让大家知道有这样一个不错的选择", "timestamp": 1636454636, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897283, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897259, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 外企钱少呀，以及难进。我是互联网专业，进微软比进字节还难", "timestamp": 1636454664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897287, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897233, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 单纯疑惑不是杠，认为某种言论是男性发出的就是对女性的刻板印象？难道不是对男性的刻板印象？", "timestamp": 1636454700, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897293, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897276, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 谢谢。但是也不能女生全赶到外企，女生也想赚钱，这不是个解决办法。", "timestamp": 1636454730, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897296, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897276, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 好的，谢谢你。", "timestamp": 1636454747, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897302, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897276, "tag": null, "text": "真正想永远规避掉这个恶心事，真的只能run了，又回到月经话题", "timestamp": 1636454777, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897303, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897287, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 女的也这样想，基本上是所有人的潜意识了。", "timestamp": 1636454782, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897304, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897283, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是吗，从我的实习工资来看钱也不算少了，互联网行业不了解", "timestamp": 1636454785, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897283, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 同为互联网，微软和google太难了555", "timestamp": 1636454788, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897311, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谷歌兼职死亡难度", "timestamp": 1636454803, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897316, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "兼职=简直", "timestamp": 1636454820, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897325, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897268, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 数学期望应该差不多吧，都是人类。有能力的男性和女性比例不应该差很多。你若是认为期望值相差很大，这不就是歧视？但所有高层或是领导者中男性确实占主导呀。", "timestamp": 1636454882, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897361, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897325, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 比如提到饭圈恶臭本能地想到女性，提到肥宅恶心本能地想到男性，这是基于这两个群体中相应性别占主导的事实。相应的，清华男女比2：1，理工科更甚，而且男女兴趣本身就存在差异，习惯性地认为某些言论是男生发出的不能叫歧视吧", "timestamp": 1636455143, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897452, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897361, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 你说得有道理。但让我思考的是，为什么宏观上男女的兴趣差异这么大。兴趣不可能是先天就形成的，那或许就是社会全人类的某些刻板印象反作用于男女，迫使他们形成了这样的分化？清华有很多很擅长理工科的女生，而喜欢文科的男生也不在少数。我不相信如果没有文化以及社会的外力，统计规律会呈现出这样的结果。\n此外我想指明一点，正如你所说是群体的特性，或许这个群体确实具有这样的特性，但具体到个体，这样类型化的认知就是不正确的。不能带着对群体的印象去认识所有人；同时，对一个人的直观认识是由性别开始，那么，为了不带有也许是错误的先验判断，最好不以性别（除此之外，国籍、人种等等）去认识一个人。", "timestamp": 1636455760, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897572, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897361, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 古代靠写文章做官吃饭的时候，就没人说女人更擅长文科男人该去搞数理，哪有那么多天生的差异，大多都是社会规训出来的", "timestamp": 1636456566, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2897581, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "世界第一个程序员叫ada，女生，只不过后来cs赚钱了又变成男生了", "timestamp": 1636456624, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2898169, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "很赞同洞里E,D,H几位，我和我身边很多男生也持类似的观点。IT类的专业可以说目前最适合希望通过奋斗实现自身价值的女生了。", "timestamp": 1636462090, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2898185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897452, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 非常赞同，说出了我想了十几年的事，但很多人对此熟视无睹。。。见过太多在理工科上有天分和兴趣的女生因为性别被师长和同龄人打压了", "timestamp": 1636462278, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2899763, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2897452, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 说得真好", "timestamp": 1636474365, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2952006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是哪家外企哇", "timestamp": 1637029931, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2967957, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 551178, "reply_to": 2898185, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 一个没见过", "timestamp": 1637161503, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 551178, "reply": 35, "tag": null, "text": "dz在某知名外企实习，同事中女性居多，薪水不错活也不多。没看出来女性的就业歧视体现在哪", "timestamp": 1636453692, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637161501, "url": "", "vote": {}}}